value.name: The Yara Gambirasio Case: Beyond Reasonable Doubt
value.original_name: Il caso Yara: oltre ogni ragionevole dubbio
value.overview: This docuseries digs into the disappearance of 13-year-old Yara and the disconcerting investigation that shattered the peace of a small Italian town.

value.name: Reasonable Doubt: A Tale of Two Kidnappings
value.original_name: Duda razonable: Historia de dos secuestros
value.overview: A fender bender that turned into a kidnapping case leads documentalist Roberto Hernández to expose the truth behind Mexico's flawed justice system.
